1
00:06,000 --> 00:11,000
Mami!

2
00:11,000 --> 00:17,000
Oči!

3
00:17,000 --> 00:22,000
Binka!

4
00:22,000 --> 00:26,000
Brina!

5
00:26,000 --> 00:31,000
No, zato bom pa napisala pismo vili straniščki.

6
00:29,619 --> 00:32,000
No, le tako dosežeš, da se kaj spremeni.

7
00:32,000 --> 00:33,890
Oranžna luč, oči.

8
00:33,890 --> 00:36,000
Ops!

7
00:36,000 --> 00:36,500
Oči!

8
00:36,500 --> 00:38,670
Zapeljal si skozi oranžno luč!

9
00:38,670 --> 00:40,500
Ja, ja, pa res.

10
00:40,500 --> 00:43,000
Je nisi videl?

11
00:43,000 --> 00:43,300
Ja, sem jo.

12
00:43,300 --> 00:46,650
A pri oranžni zmanjšaš hitrost in ustaviš.

13
00:46,650 --> 00:49,350
Zakaj nisi upočasnil in ustavil?

00:49,350 --> 00:52.352
-Ah, no, poseben primer je bil.
